						<div class="postbody">Cool, I recently made a sample player on an HSync timer and decided to add in a few more sample loops during VBlank to balance out the distortion.<br /><br />I'd recommend running a simple high-frequency square wave in your demo, and recording it to see how often and where the sample gets distorted -- you'll really notice it with a square wave.</div>

					
